# Simple Interest Project

## Project overview
A small repository with a shell script `simple-interest.sh` that calculates Simple Interest.  
This project is built to meet the final project submission requirements.

## Files
- `LICENSE` — Apache License 2.0
- `README.md` — This file
- `CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md` — Contributor guidelines
- `CONTRIBUTING.md` — How to contribute
- `simple-interest.sh` — Script to compute simple interest

## How to run
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/simple-interest-project.git
cd simple-interest-project
chmod +x simple-interest.sh
./simple-interest.sh <principal> <rate_percent> <time_years>
